Honestly, with the amount of traffic on the roads today (especially the glut of goddamn minivans, god I hate them)<br>
Performance isnt really a huge factor anymore, sure you want a little pep to pass or something, but the days of being able to get on a highway and open it up are just about completely behind us, since for 90% of the trip we will be stuck behind a million other cars that will travel slower and drive side by side across all lanes not allowing you to pass. <br>
Not to mention that the price of gas alone is just retarded and you might as well just tear your paycheque in half if you drive like Mario Andretti. Even if you dont consider a Hybrid, be sure that your next car will have no problems with blended fuels (Most vehicles wont) By 2007 All Gasoline sold here in Ontario, is required by law to have a 5% ethanol content (Will reduce emissions by some 600,000 Tons a year or something), and from the rumblings I hear thats in the works for all of North America, just in diffrent stages in the Lobby process. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.rogers.com/snowie/images/1elaarni.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://p197.ezboard.com/btabularasa19500.showUserPublicProfile?gid=neeshathenecro>Neesha the Necro</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Administrator</span><br>  Posts: 11962<br> <font color=#9999FF>(4/8/05 7:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://p197.ezboard.com/ftabularasa19500frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3818.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: so im buying a car</span><hr size=1> Buy a new Mustang.  Screw saving money on gas and saving the environment. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://p197.ezboard.com/btabularasa19500.showUserPublicProfile?gid=crowde>Crowde</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table style='Filter: Glow(Color=#9999FF,strength=2)'><tr><td><span class='usertitle'><font color=#000000><b>Moderator</span></font></td></tr></TABLE></b></span><br>  Posts: 4122<br> <font color=#9999FF>(4/8/05 7:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://p197.ezboard.com/ftabularasa19500frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topi